Linh Nga https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linh_Nga 0 Linh Nga ( LIN NAH; born 3 January 1982), also known as Lina Linh Nga, is a Vietnamese film director, film producer, actress, and screenwriter working in the United States. She is the founder of 9669 Films.
